---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 485
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
By: Philo
---
For it is absurd that a man should be forbidden to enter the temples
save after bathing and cleansing his body, and yet should attempt to
pray and sacrifice with a heart still soiled and spotted.
